entries.femaleVariant: V, come take my six.
Panam – did you check if all systems are operational?
V, eyes open! You almost turned me into a crater!
Go right through the gate, V.
Your turn, Bobby. Do you remember the jammer?
Sure do. We're on it.
Godspeed.
All down, it looks like.
I'll take the convoy to the mouth of the valley, then we can swap.
Checking.
Nitro injector – clear. Launcher's also green. We're good to go.
Then let the fun begin.
Good work.
Ey, Cass, you'll remember this – when the Aldecaldos were operating in LA on that huge contract after the earthquake…
I think I just ran over something…
Damn, it's serene out here.
Christ, Theodore, I'm not that old. But I do know the one you're talking about.
It's just your mind playing tricks on you.
Only the desert expanse can rival that star-studded void hanging over our heads.
Teddy, is there any chance that he's, you know...?
None. I'm sorry, Pan.
We have to keep moving. We're almost there.
Right – didn't that also involve a maglev tunnel?
Like, they had our folks working upstairs scooping up rocks while downstairs they were drilling the TransCon line?
We're on the right side of history, Theodore, even if we have to write it in our own blood. That's sure.
I know a pass to the north of here like you've never dreamt of.
The one near that rocky, pillar thing? What's that called?
The Pinnacle.
Yeah. Real jewel, that one.
I'm serious, it might've been a prairie dog…
Well, I sure hope our luck turns out better than that poor son-of-a-bitch's.
Prairie dogs run three times faster than that rusted tin can.
Well, you've both reassured and offended me. That's quite the feat, Theodore.
And then boom! a pack of Raffens raided the construction site. Half of our people didn't make it out alive. You think that…
Drones on intercept course!
Including some heavy sons-of-bitches. Get ready!
I see more drones on the road to the construction site.
Standard corpo security. Nothing we haven't seen before.
Shit!
Can we fix it? Right the hell now?
I don't know! Give me a minute!
It's a drivetrain – the augment was too much. Insides couldn't handle it!
There! Done!
Systems are lighting up. We're good to go!
Is everybody reading loud and clear? I've got us on a group channel.
Coming to you live from the Badlands, this is your host...
Teddy.
All right, all right. Sheesh.
Did you fire up that drone?
The little bird is humming away.
Can you control him on the go?
Don't insult me, Pan.
Gate's down. We're going in!
Something's busted! All the circuitry is dead!
Shit, there goes the main power – all systems are offline!
I'll try to work it out – but V, you need to somehow get rid of those drones!
No, no, no...! Fire in the cockpit! Goddamn power surge!
Panam, how's it looking? ETA?
You got it, can you put it out? Get the fuck out if not!
Sit tight, Bobby. We've got a situation in the panzer, but we'll rendez-vous with you shortly.
Christ, people, where are you?! I'm out here by the transmitter. What's the hold up?!
A minute! Fire's under control. Switching to emergency power. A couple of systems will be analogue, but she should be mobile.
Saul, they know we're coming! Drones deployed, headed straight for us!
We need more time, Bobby! Can you hold them off?
Do I have a choice?! Look after yourselves – ol' Bobby's got this!
Jesus Christ... Bobby?! Bobby, do you read? We have to go and--
I'm sorry, Mitch...
We can't afford to stop – not now.
Shit!
Finally! I was starting to miss you all!
Right here. Let's delta outta here!
OK, Bobby, the panzer's moving again! Hang tight, we're coming for you!
Bobby!
V, get in!
[Get out] On the drones!
Time to churn up some dust.
An Aldecaldo convoy. Now that's a sight to behold.
Mhm. And only this desert expanse can rival the star-studded void that hangs over our heads.
On the drones! You deal with the panzer!
Give me a minute! I can do this! We need the panzer – our lives depend on it!
I got just one son of a bitch left, and he's about to get a--
Militech drones. Heat incoming! Watch out for yourselves!
Go, V! Look to those drones! Get outside!
You are trespassing on property protected by Militech SiteSecure!
You have ignored all warnings and calls to halt. We have no choice but to open fire!
Turn back now. I repeat – turn your vehicles around!
Try to hit something! They certainly mean to!
Stay with it, V! Don't let them get a lock!
Trust me. They're junk.
Doing it, Panam, doing it!
They're closing, Panam!
They're headed our way, V!
We will greet them duly.
We need to wipe the corpos aside, off the road, make it across the bridge.
No more mistakes, not a one. We're damaged, so much shit has hit us already.
We can do this.
The panzer, V… it won't hold up much longer. Systems could go down any second.
We can do this, Panam, hang in there.
I know! Be ready!
I'd do anything to make it in one piece, anything. After that, I can improvise.
